content: I've also been thinking about the overall cost of the trip, and I'm trying to factor in all the expenses. In addition to the bike and accessories, like the Garmin Edge 830 and Bontrager Flare R, I spent $1,170 on other accessories, including the bike tune-up, a new water bottle cage, and a bike lock. I want to make sure I've got a good handle on all the costs involved.
